description:
Thoughts?

Yesterday we had a few posts deleted, and that’s alright. These days that confirms we’re going in the direction we need to be. Most of the posts are either fact-checked or in the process thereof. To me, when situations like this happen, that lets me know that regardless of if it’s true or not, fact-checked or fake news, they can’t have this information consolidated and out there - Better yet, we can’t put it out there.

Follow our back ups:
@NoizceEra
@Freedoms_Faction
@Factions_Of_Freedom
@Fellowship_And_Freedom
@Liberation_Legion
@Paradox_Radio

We are unable to go live on our primary account because of this. They did not specify for how long, but thankfully because we are on multiple platforms, with multiple accounts which have the ability to livestream 🙄 We’ll be alright.
